<section class="py-20 px-6 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h3 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-12" style="color: #65A30D;">
      PRE-LAUNCH CHECKLIST
    </h3>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 border-[3px] beginner-border">
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4" style="color: #65A30D;">STEP 1: CHOOSE YOUR BUILDER (15 MIN)</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Match tool to your skills</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li>‚úì Zero tech skills? Mixo ($9/mo) or Unicorn ($9/mo)</li>
          <li>‚úì Want more control? Wix ($16/mo) or Squarespace ($23/mo)</li>
          <li>‚úì Creative/design-focused? Framer ($15/mo) or Webflow ($15/mo)</li>
          <li>‚úì E-commerce? Shopify ($29/mo) + AI builder for landing pages</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">Action: Create free account on 2-3 builders. Test AI generation. Pick the one that feels easiest. Don't overthink this.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 border-[3px] beginner-border">
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4" style="color: #65A30D;">STEP 2: GENERATE YOUR SITE (30-60 MIN)</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Let AI build first draft</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li>‚úì Answer prompts: business name, industry, goals, services</li>
          <li>‚úì AI generates: homepage, about, contact pages</li>
          <li>‚úì Review content: edit mistakes, add specifics</li>
          <li>‚úì Customize design: change colors, fonts, images</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">Action: Don't aim for perfection. First version should be "good enough." You'll improve it over time. Done is better than perfect.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 border-[3px] beginner-border">
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4" style="color: #65A30D;">STEP 3: BUY CUSTOM DOMAIN (15 MIN)</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Professional URL is non-negotiable</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li>‚úì Search for yourbrand.com (or closest available)</li>
          <li>‚úì Buy through builder (easiest) or Namecheap, Google Domains</li>
          <li>‚úì Cost: $10-15/year (often free first year with builder)</li>
          <li>‚úì Connect domain to your site (builder auto-connects if bought through them)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">Action: Buy custom domain before launching. Free subdomain signals "I'm not serious." Custom domain signals "I'm in business."</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 border-[3px] beginner-border">
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4" style="color: #65A30D;">STEP 4: FILL SEO FIELDS (15 MIN)</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Help Google find you</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li>‚úì Page title: descriptive, includes business name (max 60 chars)</li>
          <li>‚úì Meta description: what your page offers (max 160 chars)</li>
          <li>‚úì Heading structure: H1 (main title), H2 (sections)</li>
          <li>‚úì Image alt text: describe images for SEO/accessibility</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">Action: Most builders have SEO tab for each page. Fill it out. "Acme Plumbing | Emergency Services in City" > "Acme Plumbing - Page 1."</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 border-[3px] beginner-border">
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4" style="color: #65A30D;">STEP 5: MOBILE PREVIEW (5 MIN)</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Test on phone before publishing</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li>‚úì Switch to mobile preview mode in builder</li>
          <li>‚úì Check: text readable? buttons clickable? images load?</li>
          <li>‚úì Fix issues: adjust font sizes, reorder sections</li>
          <li>‚úì Test on actual phone if possible (borrow friend's)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">Action: 60% of visitors are on mobile. If your site breaks on phones, you lose 60% of potential customers. Don't skip this step.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 border-[3px] beginner-border">
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4" style="color: #65A30D;">STEP 6: PROOFREAD EVERYTHING (10 MIN)</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Typos kill credibility</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li>‚úì Read all text out loud (catches awkward phrasing)</li>
          <li>‚úì Check contact info: email, phone, address correct</li>
          <li>‚úì Test all links: do they work? go to right place?</li>
          <li>‚úì Ask friend to review (fresh eyes catch mistakes)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">Action: Typos signal "I don't care about quality." Professional sites are typo-free. One thorough proofread prevents embarrassment.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 border-[3px] beginner-border">
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4" style="color: #65A30D;">STEP 7: PUBLISH & TEST (5 MIN)</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Go live, then verify</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li>‚úì Click publish (builder handles deployment)</li>
          <li>‚úì Open your site in private browser window</li>
          <li>‚úì Test: contact form works? phone number clickable?</li>
          <li>‚úì Share link with friend for final check</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">Action: Publishing is anticlimactic. Click button, wait 30 seconds, site is live. Then: celebrate. You built a website. That's huge.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 border-[3px] beginner-border">
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4" style="color: #65A30D;">STEP 8: SUBMIT TO GOOGLE (5 MIN)</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Help search engines find you</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li>‚úì Submit site to Google Search Console (free)</li>
          <li>‚úì Submit sitemap (builder auto-generates)</li>
          <li>‚úì Request indexing: "Google, add my site to search results"</li>
          <li>‚úì Verify site ownership (builder provides instructions)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">Action: Google won't find your site immediately. Submitting tells Google "I exist." Indexing takes 1-4 weeks. Do this now, reap benefits later.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-lime-50 to-green-50 p-8 border-[3px] beginner-border">
      <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2 text-xl">‚è± TIME INVESTMENT: 2 hours from zero to live website</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">Beginners overestimate complexity. <strong class="text-lime-600">Modern AI builders make launching a website take one afternoon.</strong> Follow this checklist, you'll be live by dinner. First website is hardest. Second takes 30 minutes.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
