        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Everything breaks, nothing works</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">You publish. Nobody visits. Google doesn't list you. Contact form sends messages to spam. You feel like you wasted time. Normal. Every website starts at zero. Month 1 is about fixing launch issues, not getting traffic.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Action: Fix broken links, test contact form, verify mobile display, add Google Analytics. Don't panic about traffic. That comes later.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-8 border-[3px]" style="border-color: #94A3B8;">
