        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Polish what you launched</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Month 1 reality sets in. Month 2: improve. Better photos, clearer copy, stronger calls-to-action. Add testimonials if you have them. Start blog if it makes sense. Website is never "done." It evolves.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Action: Replace placeholder content with real. Add 2-3 case studies or portfolio items. Write first blog post. Share site on social media.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-8 border-[3px]" style="border-color: #94A3B8;">
