        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Action: Use Google Search Console to see which queries find your site. Write content targeting those queries. Build 3-5 backlinks (ask friends, partners to link).</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-8 border-[3px] beginner-border">
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4" style="color: #65A30D;">MONTH 4-6: GRADUAL TRACTION</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Traffic snowball starts rolling</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Consistent content + SEO + time = organic traffic. Month 4-6: first consistent non-zero traffic. Maybe 50-200 visits/month. Doesn't sound like much? It's 50-200 more than month 0. Compound growth accelerates.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Action: Weekly content updates (blog, case studies). Monthly SEO review (keywords, rankings). Track analytics monthly. Celebrate small wins (first inquiry from website!).</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="beginner-gradient p-8 text-white text-center">
      <p class="text-3xl font-black mb-4">üéØ BEGINNER VERDICT: First website is hardest, second is easy</p>
      <p class="text-xl opacity-90">Choose simple tool (Mixo/Wix/Squarespace), follow checklist, publish imperfectly, improve over time. <strong class="text-lime-200">6 months from now, you'll wonder why you waited so long.</strong> Your website is your digital home. Build it today.</p>
    </div>
